Package: huito
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Flexible and Reproducible Label Designs
Description: The 'Huito' software is an open-source R package to deploys flexible and 
  reproducible labels using layers. The 'huito' package is part of the 'inkaverse'
  project for developing different procedures and tools used in plant science and 
  experimental designs. Learn more about the 'inkaverse' project at <https://inkaverse.com/>.
Date: 2021-11-22
